OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cold with a mix of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and frequent blustery showers,
OL,7,Fwhich will be heavy at times with a
OL,8,Frisk of thunder. Occasionally strong
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,12,Fclear spells overnight, with showers,
OL,13,Fthe showers becoming less frequent and
OL,14,Flighter. Northwesterly breeze
OL,15,Fcontinuing, locally strong in coastal
OL,16,Fparts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
