OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSunny spells and showers,
OL,6,Fperhaps cloudier in west with more
OL,7,Fpersistent rain for a time. The
OL,8,Fshowers tending to die out through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Breezy with winds turning
OL,10,Fmore northerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry with sunny spells Friday. Bright
OL,14,Fstart Saturday but becoming cloudy
OL,15,Fwith rain spreading east in afternoon.
OL,16,FRain clears overnight to leave sunny
OL,17,Fspells and a few showers Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
